                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Grasping Whirlwind gloves are mandatory.</strong>
                    <p>Without these gloves, Whirlwind's duration is too short and you lose the Dust Devil tornadoes. This unique is absolutely required &mdash; do not attempt this build without it.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Fury management is critical in low-density areas.</strong>
                    <p>Whirlwind drains Fury constantly. In sparse areas, use Lunging Strike to generate resource before spinning. Fury Cost Reduction tempering is essential for sustained spinning.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Keep shouts up at all times.</strong>
                    <p>Your three shouts provide massive offensive and defensive buffs. Rage of Harrogath reduces cooldowns significantly, so recast them immediately when available for near-permanent uptime.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Spin into packs, not around them.</strong>
